       </section> 
       <section class="section_content section editor_section"> 
        <div class="content_text content_editor"> 
         <h2 class="mid_title">Monthly Position</h2> 
        </div> 
       </section> 
       <section class="section_content section accordion_section"> 
        <div class="accordion" "> 
         <div class="card"> 
          <div class="card-header" id="heading11"> 
           <h2 class="mb-0"> <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse_11_0" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne"> Product Quality Specialist </button> </h2> 
          </div> 
          <div id="collapse_11_0" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading11" data-parent="#accordionExample"> 
           <div class="card-body"> 
            <div class="content_text content_editor"> 
             <p><b>(</b><b>5-day work week, 10 hours per day, “includes 2 sessions of 30-minute meal break”)</b></p> 
             <p><b>Job Profile:</b></p> 
             <p>As&nbsp;<b>Food Quality Specialist</b>, responsibilities include, but not limited to:</p> 
             <ul> 
              <li>Quickly and accurately produce high-quality food for customers according to product quality regulations</li> 
              <li>Participate in daily operations of the restaurant, such as preparing raw materials and keeping the restaurant clean</li> 
              <li>Ensure that production systems operate smoothly and perform all food safety steps</li> 
              <li>Follow production procedures and product standards</li> 
             </ul> 
             <p><b>Requirements:</b></p> 
             <ul> 
              <li>Hold a Secondary 3 or higher education</li> 
              <li>At least one year working experience in the catering industry</li> 
              <li>Enthusiastic with and interested in the development of the catering industry</li> 
              <li>Proactive, responsible and be a team player</li> 
              <li>Attentive willing to follow procedures and standards</li> 
              <li>Passionate in food preparation</li> 
              <li>Able to adapt shift work<a href="https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-scaled.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-5747" src="https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-scaled.jpg" alt="Overall_chat_en" width="755" height="346" srcset="https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-300x137.jpg 300w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-1024x469.jpg 1024w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-768x352.jpg 768w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-1536x703.jpg 1536w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-2048x938.jpg 2048w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-22x10.jpg 22w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-36x16.jpg 36w, https://www.mcdonalds.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Overall_chat_en-80x37.jpg 80w" sizes="(max-width: 755px) 100vw, 755px"></a></li> 
